Class GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions
  • Enclosing class:
    GasStationManager

    public static final class GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions
extends Object
    Contains information used in filtering which gas stations are returned when retrieving gas stations in a circular region.

        public GasStationsRadiusOptions(GeoPoint center,
                        double radius)
        Initializes a new instance of GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions class where the radius units depends on the user settings.

        The units for the radius is either meters or miles depending on the settings that are set using UserPreferences.

        Parameters:
        center - The center of the region where the gas stations are located.
        radius - The radius of the region where the gas stations are located.

      • setCenter

        public GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions setCenter(GeoPoint value)
        Sets the center point of the circular region.

        Northern latitudes are positive and southern latitudes are negative. Eastern hemisphere longitudes are positive and western hemisphere longitudes are negative. Longitudes in North America are negative. The latitude and longitude values are expressed using the WGS 84 datum.

        Parameters:
        value - The center of the region in which to get data.
        Returns:
        This instance of the GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions class.
        Throws:
        GasStationManager.GasStationManagerException - when the specified center point is invalid.

      • setRadius

        public GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions setRadius(double value)
        Sets the radius of the circular region.

        Any features that are fully or partially enclosed within the bounding area are selected. If the Units parameter is set to Metric, the radius is measured in meters; if Units is set to MILES, the radius is measured in miles.

        Parameters:
        value - The radius of the circular bounding area from which to return data.
        Returns:
        This instance of the GasStationManager.GasStationsRadiusOptions class.
        Throws:
        GasStationManager.GasStationManagerException - when the radius is less than or equal to zero.
